Plan update
The exploit path itself completes and leaves ~27 WETH on the verifier. The failure comes from harness accounting: `profitToken()` is `address(0)` before execution, so the test never computes the ERC20 balance delta afterward.
  ✓ Inspect verifier and test harness
  ✓ Trace exploit profit shortfall
  → Patch Solidity execution path
  • Run targeted Foundry test
